				<title>What the fuck</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13431153/scp-5286#post-4837600</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 06 Dec 2020 03:47:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>staccato_tomato</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6788172</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So I typically hold a little distaste for body horror, but when its done this damn <em>creatively</em>, I cant help but be a fan. Great first outing and I'll be looking forward to reading your future work. Good stuff. Now if you'll excuse me, its time to develop an irrational fear of miniature clones popping out of cysts&#8230;.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
