					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Came here from your reddit post, and I’m glad I did! The concept is absolutely bizarre, which is my favorite type of scip. I also love the Dionysus (?) tie-in, really brings this article to the next level. I wouldn’t say it’s one of the best scips ever or anything, but it’s overall pretty fucking solid.</p> 
				 	]]>
